- The right side `∑ i ∈ s, w i` is `∑ i ∈ s, w i`
- By `Finset.sum_attach`, `∑ x ∈ s.attach, w x = ∑ i ∈ Finset.univ, if i ∈ s then w i else 0`
- But our function `w'` is `fun i ↦ if hi : i ∈ s then w ⟨i, hi⟩ else 0`
